{"tid":2359532,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"華府國會騷亂增至五死｜檢察長：考慮起訴川普等人暴動、叛亂及煽動共謀罪","createTime":"2021-01-09T03:42:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T23:40:38.000Z","uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"44fcfb97e425120d7ea17336da2ea5c024cbb368","tid":2359532,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T03:42:57.000Z","msg":"【華府國會騷亂增至五死｜檢察長：考慮起訴川普等人暴動、叛亂及煽動共謀罪】<br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普被指煽動支持者，觸發周三（六日）華府國會的暴力衝突，大批人士攻擊警察、衝入國會，被稱為美國國會歷史二百年最大破壞，造成四名示威者死亡及一名警員Brian Sicknick殉職。共和黨有眾議員更稱川普是「試圖政變」。國會騷亂一事進一步使川普眾叛親離，川普政權的國安團隊與白宮多名成員辭職，包括副國家安全顧問博明Matthew Pottinger、運輸部長趙小蘭、教育部長 Betsy DeVos；而美國國會警察局長Steven Sund則引疚辭職。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》(Wall Street Journal)社論呼籲總統川普辭職，稱川普本應是「宣示要擁護美國法律的元首」，而這次「對立法機構的攻擊，遠超越只是拒絕認輸。就我們看來，這逾越了川普先生先前不曾逾越的憲法界線，而這是可以彈劾的；要是他能默默離開，對每個人&mdash;&mdash;包括他自己在內，都是最好的」。<br />\n<br />\n華府署理檢察長謝爾溫(Michael Sherwin)稱，考慮以暴動、叛亂及煽動共謀罪等向包括川普在內的所有參與者提出起訴。<br />\n<br />\n▋全文見： <a href=\"https://www.localpresshk.com/2021/01/capitol-violence/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2021%2F01%2Fcapitol-violence%2F&d=M%2BQ4vsyFJ%2Bls%2BsYkNkBEXdg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=638ad014\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.localpresshk.com/2021/01/capitol-violence/</a>"},{"pid":"be9f44529d180bf711a66c4894deb1f05b633d7a","tid":2359532,"uid":287422,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T03:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBurn Loot Murder就無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aa033112e2b70dee24c2447153d7f749f67f0c5","tid":2359532,"uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T03:48:08.000Z","msg":"世上根本冇民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只有利益"},{"pid":"3d6ba56446d435eeea13b868e2b95e52a2aaaafd","tid":2359532,"uid":3873,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T03:56:48.000Z","msg":"陛下何故造反<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc1cc223cd9cd84992ebfff7340683fb8062ad57","tid":2359532,"uid":370972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6aa033112e2b70dee24c2447153d7f749f67f0c5","tid":2359532,"uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T03:48:08.000Z","msg":"世上根本冇民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只有利益"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T04:02:28.000Z","msg":"一直都係。<br />\n只係啲左膠一直講大話。"},{"pid":"87366b44e566d5dc0db0880809cd540a5b2b90b3","tid":2359532,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T07:48:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349347b7c26371ee96cc9357643f55a8f27c6f9b","tid":2359532,"uid":182610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T20:16:55.000Z","msg":"點解無人聲援美國被指暴動既手足<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b38ff2153cfc72833ad946fec6c2076b4aa83d6e","tid":2359532,"uid":38572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T20:34:01.000Z","msg":"GOP 真係呢件事入面真係好廢"},{"pid":"a4b81145c6bbc3391cbf476973c1790b15df09e6","tid":2359532,"uid":147367,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T20:39:41.000Z","msg":"BLM死左幾多人，損失左幾多財產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83befaef48e3c2436d5a